The Tap Tap is a group of people with disabilities.
How do you manage these journeys logistically and organizationally?
It's not as bad as it seems at first glance.
We have five members on an electric trolley, their trolleys have to travel in the luggage compartment, and of course we drag a large amount of cargo and toolboxes with us...
